"""
!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!
!  NOTE:                                                                      !
!     the program MUST be compiled in double precision:                       !
!        LINUX:  ifort -real-size 64                                          !
!                                                                             !
